## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3392f-315">`WriteEvent`方法为重载提供字符串和整数参数的组合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3392f-315">The `WriteEvent` method provides overloads with combinations of string and integer arguments.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3392f-316">如果这些组合均不符合调用的参数, 编译器将使用<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>重载, 这比其他重载要慢得多。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3392f-316">If none of these combinations match the parameters for the call, the compiler uses the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> overload, which is considerably slower than the other overloads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3392f-317">有关详细信息, 请参阅重载页。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3392f-317">See the overload page for details.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3392f-318">在所有情况下, `eventid`该参数应大于0或小于 65535, 否则操作中可能会发生错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3392f-318">In all cases, the `eventid` parameter should be greater than 0 or less than 65535 or errors can occur in the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3392f-319">如果发生错误, 则可以通过检查调试器的输出流来获取有关错误来源的详细信息, 前提是已将调试器附加到进程触发事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3392f-319">If errors do occur, you can get more information about the source of the error by checking the output stream of the debugger, if you have a debugger attached to the process firing events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3392f-320">如果在发生错误的事件源上有 ETW 侦听器, 还可以查看 ETW 事件流中报告的错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3392f-320">You can also look for errors reported in the ETW event stream, if you have an ETW listener on the event source where the error occurs.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3392f-321">在派生类中<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>实现标识为 ETW 事件的方法时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3392f-321">When you implement a method that is identified as an ETW event in an <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>-derived class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3392f-322">您必须调用基类<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A>方法<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A> , 并将和与实现的方法相同的参数与下面的示例类似。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3392f-322">You must call the base class <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A> method passing the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A> and the same arguments as the implemented method similar to the following example.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[Event(2, Level = EventLevel.Informational)]  
public void Info1(string arg1)  
{  
 base.WriteEvent(2, arg1);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3392f-323">还可以使用<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A>方法创建自定义重载。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3392f-323">You can also create a custom overload by using the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A> method.</span></span>

  
  
